<span class="size11 darkgray">Jun 4, 2004</span>
                
                

            </div>
			<span class="anthracite size13" contentbodystyle="Anthracite">The robbery certainly doesn't mesh. Nothing was taken until that point and the knowledge that keys, jewelry, and cash were taken doesn't make sense. If you're out for money, you take the laptop, the cash and the jewelry. If you're out for trade secrets, you take the laptop and the keys. It seems too coincidental, like a sheet pulled over your eyes.</span>
		</div>
           
    <div class="spacer"></div>

    <div class="rule-gray"></div>
    <div class="spacer-small"></div>

    
